---
title: Asian Crumbed Chicken & Soy Veggies with Ginger Rice & Sesame Dressing
description: This chicken schnitzel has a fun Asian twist, with sesame seeds mixed right into the golden crumb. Serve it atop fragrant ginger rice and savoury soy veggies, with a drizzle of sesame dressing to pull it all together. Go on, grab a fork and dig right in!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66bdb06cc78425eccd8c88f5-c561f128.jpeg
